    "updated_at": "2016-09-23T22:07:45Z",
    "body": "I am able to reproduce the flashing issue with your above code.\n\nWhat if you change your code to only show the dock when it's not already visible?\n\nThis works for me with no flickering:\n\n``` js\napp.dock.hide()\n\nsetInterval(function() {\n  if (!app.dock.isVisible()) app.dock.show\n}, 1000)\n```\n"
